---
import BaseLayout from '../../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import '../../../styles/global.css';
---

<BaseLayout
  lang="en"
  dir="ltr"
  title="External Links | Dr. Haitham A. El-Ghareeb"
  description="Educational, professional, and publication-related external links"
>
  <main class="page-main">
    <section class="shell hero">
      <p class="hero__eyebrow">External Links</p>
      <h1 class="hero__title">Educational resources and externally hosted work</h1>
      <p class="hero__lead">
        This section is intended to gather useful external resources, professional links, and pages
        where books, articles, or related scholarly work are published outside the website itself.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="shell section">
      <div class="grid-two">
        <article class="content-card">
          <p class="content-card__meta">Educational resources</p>
          <h2 class="section-title">Useful links for visitors</h2>
          <p>
            The page can later host carefully selected educational and research-oriented resources
            organized by topic, audience, or purpose.
          </p>
        </article>
        <article class="content-card">
          <p class="content-card__meta">Publication access points</p>
          <h2 class="section-title">Connections to work beyond the site</h2>
          <p>
            It also provides a place for linking outward to profiles, article hosts, and publication
            pages connected with the broader scholarly presence of the site owner.
          </p>
        </article>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
